命 俾自己永遠停留係呢一刻<br />\n<br />\n當然果陣抑鬱得嚴重先會諗埋一邊  依家無論點都好都要行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"457c441bfecd1a87476e40a0333db1e930bafda4","tid":306791,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"我不是想死<br />\n而是害怕活著"},{"pid":"0e33e9936a260116363c52d045448743b2f6634f","tid":306791,"uid":32795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>理想同現實差太遠，冇希望，搵唔到出路，就想死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再加上屋企人不停問我之後點，搵咩工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵咩工又點，都唔洗自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咁多年想入會計，到依家9成9做唔到，唔知仲有咩出路<br />\n求其搵份工有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eacd002cf3a18e6bed88d934d946e675c8e98fb2","tid":306791,"uid":39733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"唔係想死<br />\n係唔想活<br />\n<br />\n問題係無<br />\n就係唔知生存為乜"},{"pid":"557fc651c61da7245d95f3020892519f8cc861fb","tid":306791,"uid":32795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自殺唔會解決到問題 但係可以解決到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係，再無煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1013ab19a46759850d596c9e9766d359ac2d06b5","tid":306791,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自殺唔會解決到問題 但係可以解決到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係，再無煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma